at my request.

51:01.805 --> 51:03.445
You will be seen as a hero...

51:04.325 --> 51:05.325
not as a criminal.

51:05.645 --> 51:06.925
And my father's debt?

51:07.125 --> 51:08.765
It remains unpaid,

51:08.965 --> 51:11.245
